```plantuml
@startuml
skinparam handwritten true

interface Aggregate {
    + Iterator iterator()
}

interface Iterator<T> {
    + boolean hasNext()
    + T next()
}

class BookShelf {
    + BookIterator iterator()
}

class BookIterator {
    - BookShelf bookShelf
    + boolean hasNext()
    + Book next()
}

Aggregate <|-- BookShelf
Iterator <|-- BookIterator
BookShelf o-- BookIterator
Aggregate --> Iterator : Creates

note top of Aggregate: 集合，用于创建Iterator迭代器接口
note bottom of BookShelf: 会创建出具体的Iterator角色
note bottom of BookIterator: 具体的迭代器，\n包含了遍历集合所必须的信息（bookShelf）

title 迭代器模式
@enduml
```
